    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. but if it's used by both sides, does that mean it's equally bad? i wonder if there's a difference between when a random person on twitter posts something wrong vs when high-level media outlets or actual political leaders use the label to attack certain reporting. is there a \"more valid\" way the term is used?",
